<?xml version="1.0"?>

<section xml:id="ch-mixed-review">
    <title>Mixed Review</title>
    <introduction>
        <p>Bring multiple CS1 concepts together in one guided review activity.</p>
    </introduction>
    <subsection>
        <title>Part A: Code Dissubsection</title>
        <exercise xml:id="ex-mixed-dissubsection">
            <statement>
                <program language="python">
def count_long_words(words):
    total = 0
    for word in words:
        if len(word) > 4:
            total = total + 1
    return total

items = ["book", "banana", "pen", "laptop"]
result = count_long_words(items)
print(result)</program>
                <p>Identify the function name, parameter, return type, loop used, condition checked, and output.</p>
            </statement>
 <response>
    </response>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>
    <subsection>
        <title>Part B: Trace</title>
        <exercise xml:id="ex-mixed-trace">
            <statement>
                <p>Complete a trace table for the program above with columns for iteration, <c>word</c>, whether <c>len(word) &gt; 4</c>, and <c>total</c>.
                </p>
            </statement>
 <response>
    </response>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>
    <subsection>
        <title>Part C: Fix</title>
        <exercise xml:id="ex-mixed-fix">
            <statement>
                <p>The code below is meant to count how many even numbers are in a list, but it has errors. Correct it.</p>
                <program language="python">
def count_evens(numbers)
    total = 0
    for num in numbers
        if num % 2 = 0:
            total = total + 1
    return total</program>
            </statement>
 <response>
    </response>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>
    <subsection>
        <title>Part D: Create</title>
        <exercise xml:id="ex-mixed-create">
            <statement>
                <p>Write a function named <c>count_a_words(words)</c> that takes a list of strings and returns how many words start with the letter <c>a</c>. Then write three test calls.</p>
            </statement>
 <response>
    </response>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>
    <subsection>
        <title>Think About ...</title>
        <exercise xml:id="ex-mixed-reflection">
            <statement>
                <p>Which topic in this worksheet felt strongest for you? Which one needs more review?</p>
            </statement>
 <response>
    </response>
        </exercise>
    </subsection>
</section>